===Noun===
'''liquorice'''

# (''countable'') A [[leguminous]] [[plant]], ''[[Glycyrrhiza glabra]]'', from which a [[sweet]] [[black]] [[liquor]] is extracted and used as a [[confection]] and in [[medicine]]
# (''uncountable'') a type of [[confection]] made from liquorice extract.

